<script>
import {wxa, Page} from '@wxa/core';
import foo from './test.js';

@Page
export default class Index {
    onLoad() {
        console.log(this);
        console.log('hello, this is wxa page');
    }
    goLog() {
        this.router.push('./log');
        // console.log('==');
    }
    onShareAppMessage() {}
}
</script>
<config lang="json">
{
    "navigationTextTitle": "首页",
    "usingComponents": {
        "vant-button": "vant-weapp/dist/button/index",
        "vant-tab": "vant-weapp/dist/tab/index",
        "vant-tabs": "vant-weapp/dist/tabs/index"
    }
}
</config>
<template>
<!-- <wxs src="../addSpace.wxs"></wxs> -->
<view class="page">
    <view class="slogn">
        hello, this is wxa!
    </view>
    <vant-button wx:if={{true}} bindtap="goLog">vant-button</vant-button>
    <view >
        <view class="h">标签</view>
        <!-- <image src="./logo-mini.png"></image> -->
        <vant-tabs class="tab" active="{{ active }}" bind:change="onChange">
            <vant-tab title="标签 1">内容 1</vant-tab>
            <vant-tab title="标签 2">内容 2</vant-tab>
            <vant-tab title="标签 3">内容 3</vant-tab>
            <vant-tab title="标签 4">内容 4</vant-tab>
        </vant-tabs>
    </view>
</view>
</template>
<style lang="css">
.page {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}

.tab {
    width: 100%;
}

view {
    width: 100%;
}
</style>
